      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not-assessed is acceptable at MRL 2 provided turbulence model selection is documented with literature justification.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on published literature demonstrating superior performance for rotating turbomachinery hemolysis prediction (Garon and Farinas, 2004). Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2."
