    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 for Model Risk Level 2 with Medium model influence and High decision consequence. CFD hemolysis predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points. The worst-case operating condition is correctly identified. Credibility assessment supports regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
